        desc: "Qt's model/view splits data (model) from display (view). For most cases use the convenience widgets `QListWidget` / `QTableWidget` (data + view in one). For real datasets or virtualization, define a `QAbstractTableModel` and pair with a `QSortFilterProxyModel` for free sorting/filtering.",
